<template>
<v-app>
  <v-content class="mx-4 mb-4">
        <Navbar />
    <router-view></router-view>
    <adminButton v-if="isAdmin"></adminButton>

import Navbar from './components/Navbar'
import adminButton from './components/adminButton'

  computed: {
    isAdmin () {

  }
}
</script>
